<text><body>
<lb n="0422b05" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0422b06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0422b07" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1304</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0422b08" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0422004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享保年間刊長谷寺藏本，【甲】康元二年寫東寺三密藏本</note>宿曜<note n="0422005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">儀軌＝軌儀【甲】</note><note n="0422005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">儀軌【大】，軌儀【甲】</note><app n="0422005"><lem wit="【大】">儀軌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">軌儀</rdg></app>一卷</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0422b09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0422b10" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="author">一行撰</byline>
<lb n="0422b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422b1101">虛空藏印　合掌縛水指。風指如寶形。真言
<lb n="0422b12" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0422b13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422b1301" cb:type="dharani">唵阿伽沙<note place="inline">一</note>迦羅波伊野<note place="inline">二</note>唵麼哩<note place="inline">三</note>伽摩哩<note place="inline">四</note>
<lb n="0422b14" ed="T"/>母梨<note place="inline">五</note>娑<note n="0422006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚩＝婆【甲】</note><note n="0422006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩【大】，婆【甲】</note><app n="0422006"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">婆</rdg></app>賀</p>
<lb n="0422b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422b1501">若人欲求福智。當歸依此菩薩。日月<note n="0422007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">星＋（宿）【甲】</note><note n="0422007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">星【大】，星宿【甲】</note><app n="0422007"><lem wit="【大】">星</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">星宿</rdg></app>。皆
<lb n="0422b16" ed="T"/>虛空藏所變也。</p>
<lb n="0422b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422b1701">文殊印　虛<note n="0422008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">空＝心【甲】</note><note n="0422008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">空【大】，心【甲】</note><app n="0422008"><lem wit="【大】">空</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">心</rdg></app>合掌。以<note n="0422009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝二火【甲】</note><note n="0422009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，二火【甲】</note><app n="0422009"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">二火</rdg></app>指各押二水甲。
<lb n="0422b18" ed="T"/>二風屈捻空端。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0422b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422b1901" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>阿<note place="inline">引入惡聲</note>味<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0422010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅＝囉【甲】＊</note><note n="0422010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅【大】＊，囉【甲】＊</note><app n="0422010"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app>吽佉左<note n="0422011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">洛＝𡀔【甲】</note><note n="0422011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">洛【大】，𡀔【甲】</note><app n="0422011"><lem wit="【大】">洛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">𡀔</rdg></app>　若求息<note n="0422012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">災字甲本作本文</note><note n="0422012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">(災)【大】，災【甲】</note><app n="0422012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">災</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">災</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0422b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422b2001">當欲<note n="0422013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">殄＝珍【甲】</note><note n="0422013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殄【大】，珍【甲】</note><app n="0422013"><lem wit="【大】">殄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">珍</rdg></app>滅七種災難。所謂日月薄<note n="0422014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">喰＝<g ref="#CB14291"/>【甲】</note><note n="0422014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喰【大】，<g ref="#CB14291"/>【甲】</note><app n="0422014"><lem wit="【大】">喰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><g ref="#CB14291"/></rdg></app>五星。
<lb n="0422b21" ed="T"/>違失常度兵賊競起。水旱不時風雨失度。惡
<lb n="0422b22" ed="T"/>臣背逆損害國民。<note n="0422015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">武＝虎ィ【原】，〔武〕－【甲】</note><note n="0422015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">武【大】，虎【校異-原】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0422015"><lem wit="【大】">武</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">虎</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>狼惡獸食噉眾生。五穀
<lb n="0422b23" ed="T"/>不登。如是災禍急厄官府王難死厄<note n="0422016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（怕）＋怖【甲】</note><note n="0422016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怖【大】，怕怖【甲】</note><app n="0422016"><lem wit="【大】">怖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">怕怖</rdg></app>等。皆
<lb n="0422b24" ed="T"/>當消散。</p>
<lb n="0422b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422b2501">普賢印　虛心合掌真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0422b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422b2601" cb:type="dharani">支波啄<note place="inline">一決定</note>毘尼波啄<note place="inline">二斷結</note>鳥蘇波啄<note place="inline">三盡生死</note></p>
<lb n="0422b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422b2701">此呪平旦誦七遍<note n="0422017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">夜＋（誦）【甲】</note><note n="0422017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夜【大】，夜誦【甲】</note><app n="0422017"><lem wit="【大】">夜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">夜誦</rdg></app>七遍。厭魅野道<note n="0422018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蟲＝蠱【甲】</note><note n="0422018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蟲【大】，蠱【甲】</note><app n="0422018"><lem wit="【大】">蟲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蠱</rdg></app>毒
<lb n="0422b28" ed="T"/>皆悉消滅。能得身心<note n="0422019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慧＝瑟【甲】</note><note n="0422019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慧【大】，瑟【甲】</note><app n="0422019"><lem wit="【大】">慧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">瑟</rdg></app>三<note n="0422020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">解＝斛【甲】</note><note n="0422020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">解【大】，斛【甲】</note><app n="0422020"><lem wit="【大】">解</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">斛</rdg></app>脫。後生不受
<lb n="0422b29" ed="T"/>生死之身。獲得法身。內外國土怨賊。一切惡
<pb n="0422c" xml:id="T21.1304.0422c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0422c01" ed="T"/>人一切鬼神一切盜賊虎狼師子毒蟲惡獸聞
<lb n="0422c02" ed="T"/>此呪聲。皆口噤閉不相惱亂。天變致厄惡夢
<lb n="0422c03" ed="T"/>災殃。百鳥怪異自然消滅。此呪功能不可說
<lb n="0422c04" ed="T"/>盡。</p>
<lb n="0422c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422c0501">延命印　左手捻火指空指。如持蓮花。右手
<lb n="0422c06" ed="T"/>直<note n="0422021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">申＝延【甲】</note><note n="0422021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">申【大】，延【甲】</note><app n="0422021"><lem wit="【大】">申</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">延</rdg></app>如垂。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0422c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422c0701" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>摩折<app type="star" corresp="#0422010"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app>喻碎<note place="inline">某甲</note>娑嚩<note n="0422022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">賀＝訶【甲】＊</note><note n="0422022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賀【大】＊，訶【甲】＊</note><app n="0422022"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">訶</rdg></app></p><p xml:id="pT21p0422c0713" rend="inline">若誦此呪
<lb n="0422c08" ed="T"/>延命除<note n="0422023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">災字甲本作本文</note><note n="0422023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">(災)【大】，災【甲】</note><app n="0422023"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">災</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">災</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0422c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422c0901">帝釋天印　右手作拳安腰。左<note n="0422024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">手＋（五指）【甲】</note><note n="0422024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">手【大】，手五指【甲】</note><app n="0422024"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">手五指</rdg></app>直豎相著。
<lb n="0422c10" ed="T"/>地水二指屈中節。以風著火背。屈空中節。真
<lb n="0422c11" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0422c12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422c1201" cb:type="dharani">唵因捺<app type="star" corresp="#0422010"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app>野娑嚩<app type="star" corresp="#0422022"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">訶</rdg></app></p><p xml:id="pT21p0422c1209" rend="inline">若誦此呪授與官位。
<lb n="0422c13" ed="T"/>滿足所求。</p>
<lb n="0422c14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422c1401">毘沙門天印　虛心合掌。交二空並竪。二風
<lb n="0422c15" ed="T"/>付二火側。如鉤端相去一寸不著。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0422c16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422c1601" cb:type="dharani">唵吠室羅縛拏野娑嚩<app type="star" corresp="#0422022"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">訶</rdg></app></p><p xml:id="pT21p0422c1611" rend="inline">若誦此呪得大
<lb n="0422c17" ed="T"/>富饒。晝夜守護。</p>
<lb n="0422c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422c1801">日天真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0422c19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422c1901" cb:type="dharani">曩<note n="0422025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">謨＝莫【甲】</note><note n="0422025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謨【大】，莫【甲】</note><app n="0422025"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0422010"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app>怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛羅夜<note place="inline">引</note>野曩莫<note n="0422026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">索里＝素哩【甲】</note><note n="0422026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">索里【大】，素哩【甲】</note><app n="0422026"><lem wit="【大】">索里</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">素哩</rdg></app>野
<lb n="0422c20" ed="T"/>薩嚩曩乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>怛<app type="star" corresp="#0422010"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>羅<note n="0422027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若＝惹【甲】</note><note n="0422027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若【大】，惹【甲】</note><app n="0422027"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">惹</rdg></app>野唵<note place="inline">引</note>阿謨
<lb n="0422c21" ed="T"/>伽<note n="0422028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">烏＝寫【甲】</note><note n="0422028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">烏【大】，寫【甲】</note><app n="0422028"><lem wit="【大】">烏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">寫</rdg></app><note place="inline">名位</note>設底娑嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0422c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422c2201">月天真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0422c23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422c2301" cb:type="dharani">唵戰<note place="inline">上</note>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note>曩乞灑<note place="inline">二合引</note>怛羅<note place="inline">二合</note><app type="star" corresp="#0422010"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉</rdg></app><note n="0422029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惹＝若【甲】</note><note n="0422029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惹【大】，若【甲】</note><app n="0422029"><lem wit="【大】">惹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">若</rdg></app>
<lb n="0422c24" ed="T"/>野<note place="inline">名位</note>設底娑嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0422c25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0422c2501">火<note n="0422030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">星＝天【甲】＊</note><note n="0422030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">星【大】＊，天【甲】＊</note><app n="0422030"><lem wit="【大】">星</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">天</rdg></app>真言曰。</p>
